Where you want to get that connection is unclear. One possibility would be to get it from the underlying Hibernate `Session` used by the `EntityManager`. With JPA 1.0, you&#39;ll have to do something like this:

    Session session = (Session)em.getDelegate();
    Connection conn = session.connection();

